BlockBeats news, on October 10, according to Trader T monitoring, yesterday's US spot Bitcoin ETF net outflow was updated to 40.5 million US dollars, including:


· IBIT inflow of 13.91 million US dollars;
· ARKB outflow of 44.47 million US dollars;
· BITB outflow of 9.94 million US dollars.

BlockBeats news, on October 9, Babylon announced that Cap-2 has been completed, with a total of nearly 23,000 BTC (22,891 BTC) staked. The relevant data is as follows:


Delegation: 12,960;


Stakers: 12,570;


Total fee: 1.56 BTC.


Babylon reminds users that any stakes starting from block 864800 have overflowed, please be sure to unbind and withdraw the overflowed stakes as soon as possible.
